%p
  %strong
    Q:
  %i
    What content is offered on this website for free?
  %br
  %strong
    A:
  For any referee within a league the IRDP has a contract with, all content is free and the Head Referee test is offered for a small fee. For any referee within a league the IRDP has not contracted with, the Scorekeeper content and Goal referee content is offered for free along with a sneak peek at our five pilar guides. These referees may purchase access to Assistant, Snitch, and Head referee training resources for $5USD, and the Head referee written test will be available for $20USD.  

